      <title>印尼盾贬值 印尼承诺“坚决”捍卫货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/indonesia-pledges-to-guard-currency-boldly-as-rupiah-weakens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼央行干预外汇市场，承诺坚决守护印尼盾，印尼盾已跌至四个多月来的最低水平。]]></description>
