      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 01:39:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国一年期国债收益率自 2009 年以来首次降至 1%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/china-one-year-yield-sinks-toward-1-as-policy-easing-bets-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易员加大对货币宽松的押注，中国短期债券收益率进一步下跌，自全球金融危机以来首次触及 1% 的心理关口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/china-one-year-yield-sinks-toward-1-as-policy-easing-bets-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 01:34:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索尼创纪录的股价上涨让投资者对游戏行业更加看好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/sony-s-record-climb-makes-investors-more-bullish-on-gaming-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[索尼集团公司 (Sony Group Corp.) 期待已久的股价创下历史新高，鼓舞了看涨的投资者和分析师，他们预计，由于视频游戏前景强劲，其涨势将延续到 2025 年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/sony-s-record-climb-makes-investors-more-bullish-on-gaming-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
